<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Anzu Aero | Contact & Partnerships</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            var(--text-main): #f8fafc;
            --text-muted: #94a3b8;
            --accent: #22d3ee;
            --accent-glow: rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.4);
            --border-glass: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            --border-accent: rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.3);
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #f8fafc;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.8;
            background-image: 
                linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
                linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
                linear-gradient(135deg, #091024 0%, #172a6c 50%, #0e6b72 100%);
            background-size: 30px 30px, 30px 30px, cover;
            background-attachment: fixed;
            background-position: center center;
        }

        header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px 50px;
            background: rgba(9, 16, 36, 0.6);
            backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-glass);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--accent-glow);
        }

        .logo span {
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        nav a {
            color: #f8fafc;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-left: 30px;
            font-weight: 500;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
        }

        nav a:hover, nav a.active {
            color: var(--accent);
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent);
            text-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--accent-glow);
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1050px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .section {
            background: rgba(15, 25, 50, 0.45);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-glass);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .section:hover {
            border-color: var(--border-accent);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        h2 {
            color: var(--accent);
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-glass);
            padding-bottom: 15px;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .info-item {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .info-item strong {
            display: block;
            color: var(--accent);
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .info-item p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            color: #e2e8f0;
        }

        .partner-highlight {
            background: rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.05);
            border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
            color: #94a3b8;
            background: rgba(9, 16, 36, 0.8);
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border-glass);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            header { flex-direction: column; gap: 15px; padding: 20px; }
            nav a { margin: 0 10px; font-size: 0.9rem; }
            .container { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <div class="logo">ANZU <span>AERO</span></div>
        <nav>
            <a href="index.html">Home</a>
            <a href="contact.html" class="active">Contact & Partners</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        
        <!-- Contact Information Section -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2>Contact Information</h2>
            
            <div class="info-item">
                <strong>Lead Researcher & Founder</strong>
                <p>Ahmed</p>
            </div>

            <div class="info-item">
                <strong>Email Address</strong>
                <p>Ahmed.alsulaimawi@AnzuAero.quest</p>
            </div>

            <div class="info-item">
                <strong>Phone & WhatsApp</strong>
                <p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;">+964 787 666 2111</p>
            </div>

            <div class="info-item">
                <strong>Headquarters (Founding Stage)</strong>
                <p>Fahmi Al-Mudarris St., Shaab City,<br>Al-Rusafa, Baghdad, Iraq.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Partnerships Section -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2>Strategic Partnerships</h2>
            <p style="color: #cbd5e1; font-size: 1.05rem;">Anzu Aero is currently exploring strategic collaborations to transition our conceptual research into advanced prototyping and production phases.</p>
            
            <div class="partner-highlight">
                <strong>Military Industrialization Commission of Iraq</strong>
                <p style="margin-top: 10px; font-size: 0.95rem; color: #cbd5e1;">We are currently in the preliminary negotiation phase with the Commission to discuss avenues of joint cooperation specifically focused on the development and evaluation of the "Anzu" stealth UAV project.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 Anzu Aero. All rights reserved by Lead Researcher Ahmed.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
